{"tid":890331,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"跑步跑到腳板底痛","createTime":"2018-11-05T08:42:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-05T16:22:18.000Z","uid":147710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"52872856d9ff2a88a9bfd1d6b57f7497a0a9ae1f","tid":890331,"uid":147710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T08:42:33.000Z","msg":"我一星期大概跑3-5次 每次就5公里至7公里不等 <br />\n<br />\n次次跑完隻腳板底都會痛幾日 有冇巴打有一樣情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問下係隻鞋問題定跑步姿勢錯導致<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0864ac4c21fdc0cce6fe8ae88e0acedde581e92","tid":890331,"uid":104239,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:01:04.000Z","msg":"好大機會系鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef39056cc24cb935b68e3dec8c906fc8f8ddaf42","tid":890331,"uid":159518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:02:01.000Z","msg":"鞋or鞋墊唔啱"},{"pid":"b93401a91d5df6e32e2d451bee95e8730ff753e8","tid":890331,"uid":147367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:02:47.000Z","msg":"腳弓位痛？"},{"pid":"69b81fb3a95a3b01ade55dbe64d3cf7149125f4f","tid":890331,"uid":147710,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b93401a91d5df6e32e2d451bee95e8730ff753e8","tid":890331,"uid":147367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:02:47.000Z","msg":"腳弓位痛？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:09:03.000Z","msg":"係 同埋我有扁平足"},{"pid":"177a47bd0cd1ab2e144c18f0bea8f43e0405d731","tid":890331,"uid":147710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef39056cc24cb935b68e3dec8c906fc8f8ddaf42","tid":890331,"uid":159518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:02:01.000Z","msg":"鞋or鞋墊唔啱"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:09:56.000Z","msg":"巴打有冇跑鞋推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9275cd0ce99afb9a428974b6c85ec4c2f95520be","tid":890331,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:10:41.000Z","msg":"對鞋老化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e105ccb5836d2569ea13b59af3946d7522e8f0c0","tid":890331,"uid":147367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69b81fb3a95a3b01ade55dbe64d3cf7149125f4f","tid":890331,"uid":147710,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b93401a91d5df6e32e2d451bee95e8730ff753e8","tid":890331,"uid":147367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:02:47.000Z","msg":"腳弓位痛？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:09:03.000Z","msg":"係 同埋我有扁平足"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:12:00.000Z","msg":"對跑鞋係咪中間收窄左？<br />\n我之前試過，最後換返對中間無收窄就無事"},{"pid":"9391d7c6a7e71e6e7db1f2a013aaa5e06e65bc09","tid":890331,"uid":159518,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"177a47bd0cd1ab2e144c18f0bea8f43e0405d731","tid":890331,"uid":147710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef39056cc24cb935b68e3dec8c906fc8f8ddaf42","tid":890331,"uid":159518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:02:01.000Z","msg":"鞋or鞋墊唔啱"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:09:56.000Z","msg":"巴打有冇跑鞋推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:21:20.000Z","msg":"呢樣野好複雜喎<br />\n唔講價錢同款<br />\n先要睇你有冇咩扁平足、高弓足，<br />\n再睇你平時跑步係前掌、中掌定腳跟落地<br />\n再要睇你係快、中定慢腳<br />\n平時10k 40分以下、45、50、60、75介紹既鞋已經好唔同<br />\n最後至睇牌子同對鞋既物資技術"},{"pid":"534502de8596599c0a05ed01c060fb63dab46f34","tid":890331,"uid":50088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:22:15.000Z","msg":"有機會係鞋/鞋墊/問題或者足底筋膜炎<br />\n但好老實冇認真做過檢查好難答到你咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但肯定既係一定有問題導致你而家隻腳承受唔到呢個里數/速度嘅負荷<br />\n樓主可以試下做既就試下減速加/或里數到一個跑完唔痛/一日散既地步<br />\n之後再慢慢令你隻腳去適應承受到你原本而家呢個負荷<br />\n<br />\n但如果你想快快手搞掂/或者你去到某個地步已經加負荷加得好慢但都係一加就痛既話<br />\n我建議你就最好搵個物理治療師check check啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30725588cf6bb3d7aa9c60bd6ba28594f4b5752f","tid":890331,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T16:22:18.000Z","msg":"試吓跟呢個網一步步做<br />\n搵適合自已嘅鞋<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.myprecisionfit.com/#!/page/0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.myprecisionfit.com%2F%23%21%2Fpage%2F0&d=wM3bPP5psT4qZB%2BIA%2FDayi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=7b3a7ab8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.myprecisionfit.com/#!/page/0</a>"}]}